The paper discusses the need for transparency in predictive systems based on Machine Learning algorithms, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses interpretability and explainability methods, which are important topics in Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of Interactive Machine Learning for improved transparency involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses potential limitations and caveats of interactive explainers, which could fall under the category of Cybersecurity (cs.CY) or Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
